  "texts": [
    "As a result, their proposed multimodal did not outperform the model with textual-based features.",
    "This shows that textual features are still considered pioneering in detecting rumors.",
    "Table II provides a brief summary of Arabic fake news detection studies.",
    "V. ARABIC FACT-CHECKING WEBSITESWhen researchers build datasets for fake news detection, they mostly rely on fact-checking websites.",
    "Fact-checking websites can be defined as platforms that evaluate the veracity of claims and information spread over social media networks, web articles, and public statements [95]."
